descriptionHtml:
Drangle is my third male and i think its an improvement on my other male preset, his hair i used is apaachiskyhair but you do not need it to use him, the pics have no enb so you can see it raw with no tricks to make him look better. I took some time to change his appearance but for male orcs its not that easy to do, i did my best with this one and i like the way he turned out, i hope you do aswell.

The armour he is wearing is Ashara Princes of the Woods armour which you can get [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/18008/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/18008/?[/url]

To instal him just use MO or NMM as i have already done the file path needed for an easy install, saves you time.

For my other creations i will put a link

I will be doing more texture and preset mods in the future, i do get better with each one, i just hope that some people like them if not then there is no harm done as not everyone likes the same stuff, i do makes these for my game and i choose to share them so the few that use them can have a choice in what they want their skyrim to look like, after all skyrim is a fantasy game and anything is possible with fantasy.

If you want to make him a follower go ahead, if you want to upload funny screenshots of him on this page go ahead
